i don't really know what to say i mean i really like my best guy friend and i mean we've already made things clear about us so i really dont' know what to do?! i mean i really don't get the chance to talk to him that much but when i do it's like the whole world just stops for hours on end! it's the greatest feeling! it just kills me that idk what to do about it i mean i don't wanna jeporidize our friendship but he could really be the one for me i mean think about it i've been through so much with him and i can't bare to see him get hurt so i really don't know how to get over the fact that he's back with his ex-girlfriend and i mean there is nothing that i can do or say that will change his mind about staying with her! don't get me wrong i don't want to hurt either of them but they've already dated so like honestly they need to try something new and stray away from eachother! idk apparently she makes him happy but i mean 1) he's going to college 2) they are already fighting! that's never good i don't really know how to feel right now so i guess i'm just gonna go on with my life wondering what if this happened how much would my life changed!? idk
